sequenceDiagram
  participant T as Technician
  participant Tool as psb_factory_tui
  participant Board as Board (Modbus)

  Note over T,Board: after cal exit-cal, mode = Normal

  T->>Tool: ch <n>
  T->>Tool: target <V>
  Tool->>Board: write configured target voltage
  T->>Tool: output on
  Tool->>Board: enable output, ramp to target

  T->>Tool: measure
  Tool->>Board: read channel info
  Tool-->>T: Vmeas / Imeas / target / status
  T->>T: compare against reference meter

  T->>Tool: output off
  Tool->>Board: graceful disable
